getCallMethodName(callNode:Object)→string|null|null|extract method name from CallExpression callee
extractStringValue(node:Object)→string|null→templateToString|null→templateToString|extract string from Literal or TemplateLiteral|replaces $N placeholders
templateToString(tplNode:Object)→string|convert TemplateLiteral AST node to string with $N
